      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/620466692_18558151774007943_8382149734095270294_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_s1080x1080_sh2.08&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxNTk1MDc5OTE2MzM5NTE2Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=nSYVyCKq8JEQ7kNvwGl-Ztv&amp;_nc_oc=AdqtHDc7igCdQl7VQ3_btFDbIQ3k9g6jNYw6Cnvq2JXca-u7ZNldolgipvdEVRLBzGw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=iRCk12iAaq8Ki-BpF_-LOg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzjteuxOdHoOd8oHCEi-2G4AXZEVsgsZ1LvZJL1qUCZug&amp;oe=69CA0CD7" alt="Slide 1 fra @darkmattersstudio" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/621209240_18558151783007943_4110863127445835295_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_s1080x1080_sh2.08&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxNTk1MDc5OTE2MzM5ODc4NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=5ohx6Lyiu0wQ7kNvwG5q3Vg&amp;_nc_oc=AdpguKvyAroC8k_nv7Nt20x34s0Q_K3_hRe03Pt0HRcSni5hnfxL3pC5Wgv2S8tqhPs&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=iRCk12iAaq8Ki-BpF_-LOg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfysvUIHZW53YJLOOrB_jzuJkR9Arrre4G5na02iZBxX1w&amp;oe=69CA0338" alt="Slide 2 fra @darkmattersstudio" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619604995_18558151792007943_495334721475985058_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_s1080x1080_sh2.08&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxNTk1MDc5OTA1NDM0Mzc4MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=qEyCTXSOL-kQ7kNvwFT4RMS&amp;_nc_oc=AdqKQZN7vnWyyZguDs8SIyWsg9ItN42eRK7lDusJVB5u28BuXSyurDYmwiPRciFhhOg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=iRCk12iAaq8Ki-BpF_-LOg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afz_5A1NtrsYjmwGoM1P8fOqS2ljo8qcMs4B8SM3zCLLQQ&amp;oe=69CA2891" alt="Slide 3 fra @darkmattersstudio" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619200730_18558151801007943_6916016234177559133_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_s1080x1080_sh2.08&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxNTk1MDc5OTE2MzM2MDE3Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=BAT5Lz0BmokQ7kNvwG4ffjb&amp;_nc_oc=AdpJajHhuPdEW9JkyeA55qw2kvGUrVXoIOqFJ09qByBqkKT_p13WrgmdV_AKnxPneas&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=iRCk12iAaq8Ki-BpF_-LOg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afwp_478Vzg1951PSj4dvLhKt9RGandA_c3_UkFRFi8qpA&amp;oe=69CA1984" alt="Slide 4 fra @darkmattersstudio" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (5 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@darkmattersstudio</strong></p><p>Last Thursday marked the completion of the comprehensive and sensitive restoration of the Court Theatre at Christiansborg, and the unveiling of the new exhibitions and interpretive elements. The occasion was celebrated in the presence of H.M. Queen Margrethe and H.M. Queen Mary.<br/>
<br/>
As part of the project, JAC Studios, Dark Matters, and Fortheloveoflight have, through a close interdisciplinary collaboration, developed a new interpretive approach in which architecture, light, sound, and storytelling are conceived as a single, unified experience. With respect for the listed building, the Court Theatre has been activated both as a historical artifact and as a living stage.<br/>
<br/>
This has been a rare and privileged project at the intersection of restoration, performing arts, interpretation, and design, realized in close collaboration with the Theatre Museum at the Court Theatre, Slots og kulturstyrelsen, foundations, and a strong team of specialists.<br/>
<br/>
The Theatre Museum at the Court Theatre will reopen to the public on Saturday, 7 March 2026.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you<br/>
@teatermuseet <br/>
@augustinusfonden <br/>
@apmollerfonde <br/>
@aageogjohannelouishansenfonden<br/>
<br/>
Photo by <br/>
Tine Bek <br/>
and <br/>
Kongehuset.dk</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DT0-wrgAKqX/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
