      <title>We are looking for a new colleague! About you: Experience with After Effects and...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/C6dwBoBCrQa/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6dwBoBCrQa/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/499885771_723911263485554_2194340669845886776_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzM1OTA1MjExNTAwNzQxOTQxOA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjU0MHg5NjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=QlJbrNZKpg0Q7kNvwF6hrrI&amp;_nc_oc=AdrLbkmiJ1V5TpNhPSEObgwkKjgl5anJnDS7MCOlL4YctvmK200AYo_DiCCPZbPQ4Vk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=iRCk12iAaq8Ki-BpF_-LOg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy2Qi4KxxlugS9jkFM1rXgFp9TOpeptEOjg3RgOtfx2jQ&amp;oe=69CA0726" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @darkmattersstudio" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@darkmattersstudio</strong></p><p>We are looking for a new colleague!<br/>
<br/>
About you:<br/>
Experience with After Effects and the Adobe suite is a requirement.<br/>
You must also have worked with 3D software, preferably Houdini or similar, to a degree where you have both experience with animation, rendering and possibly modelling.<br/>
<br/>
Interested in art, history, design, motion graphics and general graphic design.<br/>
<br/>
Experience in Touch Designer, Unity, Unreal programs and general interactive design will be considered a great advantage.<br/>
If you have other qualities/skills that fit our profile, we will always include them as opportunities in future projects.<br/>
<br/>
You will get to work on a wide range of exciting projects, where you often dive into areas you have never been before. We run a very flat structure in the studio, i.e. we are all together from start to finish on almost all tasks. The digital is often the cornerstone of most tasks. Still, research on how to take over an entire concert hall with plastic ivy, build a 4m high iceberg or physically find all the furniture from Hammershøi&#x27;s pictures, is not unusual in our everyday life.<br/>
<br/>
About Dark Matters<br/>
We are a creative studio that creates unique universes and visually aesthetic experiences through light, architecture, storytelling and technology.<br/>
Dark Matters works across media with exhibition design, installations, concert visuals and projections – in artistic as well as commercial arenas.<br/>
We are a small team with a busy but informal working environment in the middle of Nørrebro / Copenhagen.<br/>
<br/>
Read more about us at www.darkmatters.dk and send a short application with attached CV and visual portfolio to Lasse Andersen at lasse@darkmatters.dk</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m82/AQNBf2bhRTrzPEUjV-65SQd2L2ZOfagYNWGFT-nDcHux_ClfF6mViNEkz10P2ZkCgqqFNl2hk6Qy-EQwYdAuH1vgMmp6MXWNkxitT8c.mp4?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=nZm4Npc8CtQQ7kNvwGCyCZ-&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6NDYwNjMyMTU2NDgwMTM0LCJhc3NldF9hZ2VfZGF5cyI6NjkyLCJ2aV91c2VjYXNlX2lkIjoxMDA5OSwiZHVyYXRpb25fcyI6MzAsInVybGdlbl9zb3VyY2UiOiJ3d3cifQ%3D%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=5a92ebfb7ccf7c2f&amp;_nc_vs=HBkcFQIYT2lnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfcHJvZC82RDREQkJEOTZGRTVGN0RDNTYyMUZENjQ3Njk0NDdBRV92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAKAAYABsCiAd1c2Vfb2lsATEScHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmVfcmVjaXBlATEVAAAmjIr5gKm80QEVAigCQzMsF0A-AAAAAAAAGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX-B2XmnQEA&amp;_nc_gid=iRCk12iAaq8Ki-BpF_-LOg&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Afxdglm2pfF2BVZzQSC_RyleH5dgUsXLGS65bnVLq0hBUg&amp;oe=69C60D46">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6dwBoBCrQa/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
